Title: Double Jeopardy
Plot: SG-1 must rescue an alien world from the Goa'uld -- with help from an unexpected source. Teal'c seeks revenge on the System Lord Cronus for the murder of his father.
GuestStars: Jay Brazeau, Ron Halder, Matthew Harrison, Belinda Waymouth, Bill Croft, Tracy Hway, John DeSantis, Michael Jonsson, Paul Stafford
